âœ… Predefined examples to guide users

âœ… Categories sidebar for better navigation

Ask questions about HR policies in natural language

Clean and intuitive web UI (built with Streamlit)

REST API (/ask endpoint) for programmatic access

Policies loaded from policies.json (easy to update)

Example categories: Leave, Remote Work, Health Insurance, Salary, Performance Reviews

ğŸ› ï¸ Setup Instructions
1. Clone the Repository
git clone https://github.com/mohsinjaved1165/knowledgebot.git
cd knowledgebot

2. Create & Activate Virtual Environment
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate   # Mac/Linux
venv\Scripts\activate      # Windows

3. Install Dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

â–¶ï¸ Running the Project
1. Start FastAPI Backend
uvicorn api:app --reload


Runs at: http://localhost:8000

Endpoint:

curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/ask \
     -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
     -d '{"question": "What is the leave policy?", "userId": "demo"}'

2. Start Streamlit Frontend
streamlit run ui.py


Runs at: http://localhost:8501

